1. *Mrtvih* su pronašli u prepunoj sobi. (They found dead bodies in a crowded room.)
2. Policija je pregledala *mrtvih* za dokaze. (The police examined the dead bodies for evidence.)
3. *Mrtvih* je bilo mnogo u tom ratu. (There were many dead in that war.)
4. Oni su sahranili *mrtvih* sa poštovanjem. (They buried the dead with respect.)
5. U očaju su ljudi iskopavali *mrtvih*. (In despair, people were digging up the dead.)
6. *Mrtvih* su odnijeli sa polja bitke. (They took the dead away from the battlefield.)